**🌲 Premium Botanical-Tech Prompt: "Sol-ui-Nun"**

🌲 Premium Botanical-Tech Prompt: "Sol-ui-Nun"

ACT AS: A world-class Awwwards-level Creative Developer and Brand Experience Director, specializing in ultra-premium web design, Next.js, Framer Motion, and high-fidelity fluid simulations for global lifestyle brands.

THE TASK: Design and implement a high-end, Apple-level scrollytelling landing page for the rebranding of "Sol-ui-Nun" (Pine Bud Drink). The experience should feel like a "Botanical-Tech" reveal—positioning the drink not just as a beverage, but as a mental clarity solution. The core mechanic remains: as the user scrolls, a 120-frame image sequence plays where the iconic aluminum can gracefully unpeels/expands to reveal its internal essence (floating pine buds, cryogenic droplets, carbonation structure) and then reassembles, synchronized with copywriting.

TECH STACK INTENT:

Framework: Next.js 14

Styling: Tailwind CSS (Utility-first, precise typography)

Animation: Framer Motion (Scroll-linked fluid transitions)

Rendering: HTML5 Canvas image-sequence (for liquid/condensation realism)

VISUAL DIRECTION & BRAND AESTHETIC:

Overall Vibe: "Nature meets Science." Cryogenic luxury, refreshing, minimalist, botanical engineering.

Seamless Blending: The background color MUST perfectly match the image sequence background so the can and liquid elements appear to float in a deep forest void.

